&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;1-what-is-taso&quot;&gt;1. What is TASO?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;h4 id=&quot;taso-is-the-framework-which-optimizes-the-computation-graphs-of-dnn-models-using-automatically-generated-and-verified-graph-transformations&quot;&gt;TASO is the framework which optimizes the computation graphs of DNN models using automatically generated and verified graph transformations.&lt;/h4&gt;
